## âœ¨ Features

- ðŸ”¹ Summarizes long text inputs using AI.
- ðŸ”¹ Includes dummy text for easy testing.
- ðŸ”¹ Responsive UI for both desktop and mobile users.
- ðŸ”¹ Displays loading spinner while processing requests.

