## ðŸ’» Technology Stack

### Frontend:
- HTML5  
- CSS3  
- JavaScript  

### Backend:
- Node.js  
- Express.js  

### API:
- Hugging Face BART Model (for text summarization)

---

## ðŸš€ Getting Started

### Prerequisites
- Node.js and npm installed
- Hugging Face API token

### Setup Instructions

```bash
# Step 1: Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/palak-arora31/AI-Text-Summarizer-Web-App.git
cd AI-Text-Summarizer-Web-App

# Step 2: Add your Hugging Face API token
echo ACCESS_TOKEN=your_hugging_face_api_token > .env

# Step 3: Run the backend server
node index.js
